name: The King's Dreams: He Saw It First
description:
Looking beyond the rocks and the sea surface, an undertone of light reflected.
Many had battled the waves and struggled with their might but only those with true maritime eyes could see the way.
The path was well lit.
A Captain at the helm with more than first and second sight.
This journey was undertaken from a sleepy bliss. But he saw it well. He saw it clear and he saw it first.
